Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.52,0:23:36.52,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(1890,40)\fad(200,200)}拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:51.99,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(1890,40)\fad(200,200)}请不要惊讶  听听我的心愿吧
